al elements to the arthit-tara experience.", "experiences/1/jobLocation": "68 Sukhumvit 26, Bangkok 10110", "experiences/1/jobStartedOn": "1-2013", "experiences/1/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/1/title": "General Manager", "experiences/2/companyName": "Maddog Corporation Company Limited", "experiences/2/jobDescription": "my belief :\nthe success of each company is the ability not only to participate the needs and expectations of the customers but also to communicate them to our staff so they can provide exceptional service, it is imperative that we utilise training as a tool to remain competitive in the market.  please do not wait until problems occur because it is so hard to solve.\nbackground :\ni started my career as a trainer in 2009, after working with four seasons group for 12 years.  as a sales manager and director of social affairs and liaison, i have gained a lot of experience in hospitality.\nmy past experienced of training :\n+ Gaysorn plaza [2009] for concierge, building attendance, housekeeping & doorman\n+ Gaysorn plaza for sales & marketing department\n+ Gaysorn plaza for some tenants in the building\n+ Domus condominium - sukhumvit 16 [2009]\n+ Doctor Younger\n+ Dermalogica\n+ Dr murad\n+ Ootoya restaurant\n+ V Villa Huahin\n+ St. Andrews International School, samakee for thai teachers\n+ PMT The hour glass\n+ Pendulum\n+ Susco public company", "experiences/2/jobStartedOn": "10-2009", "experiences/2/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/2/title": "Servicing Standard Trainer", "experiences/3/companyName": "Maddog Corporation Company Limited", "experiences/3/jobLocation": "68 Sukhumvit 26, Bangkok 10110", "experiences/3/jobStartedOn": "1-2008", "experiences/3/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/3/title": "Consultant", "experiences/4/companyName": "Arthit-Tara/ Vimala Suite", "experiences/4/jobStartedOn": "2012", "experiences/4/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/4/title": "General Manager", "experiences/5/companyId": "163883", "experienc